xfy.fakeview.library.translator

类 FLayoutParamsTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • xfy.fakeview.library.translator.FLayoutParamsTranslator

  • public class FLayoutParamsTranslator
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by XiongFangyu on 2017/11/8. Translate LayoutParams into FLayoutParams If your custom LayoutParams need to be translated, the method registerTranslator(Class, Class) must be invoked before.
